-- Noir --

Noir looks back at the lizard and his slightly muffled voice, and a 
fleeting edge of a smile crosses the corner of her mouth. "OK."

She dumps out the container she'd been looking in, and then finding 
nothing, she slides it over to the collection of checked containers. 
Then she grabs another box, and finds one sitting on top, "Got 
another." She tosses it into the collection box.
